      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.5333334447
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.5470527333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "うう、暑い……こーんな太陽ギラギラの中で\n今日は何するんでしたっけ？",
      "startTime": 17.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.9138559979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "もっと大きくなってもらうために……肥料を撒く……\nこの作業が収穫の、鍵になる……",
      "startTime": 24.2913475821,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3755.8412085000014,
          "startTime": 28.0471887906
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.5138559979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "えいっ！　……こうやって撒けばいいかな？\n大きくなーれ！　大きくなーれ！",
      "startTime": 31.566803376,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5143.038479299999,
          "startTime": 36.7098418553
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1765090626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃっ。元気に育つんですよー\nこころ達にお世話してもらうなんてVIP待遇ですねー",
      "startTime": 40.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8243773144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。こころちゃん、苗達のこと好きになった？",
      "startTime": 44.8243773144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6292980831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないじゃないですかぁ\n企画失敗を避けるためですー！",
      "startTime": 52.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達がせっかく頑張って田植えしたのに、枯れたら\n意味ないですから。ホント手がかかって大変ですよー",
      "startTime": 58.366666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9306812923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……口には出さないけど、相当気に入ってる……\n寮でも……山形に行く日を、気にしてた",
      "startTime": 68.2973475297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9973479589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！　なんだかんだ言って\n愛着が湧いてきてるなーって思ったもん！",
      "startTime": 75.3493881703,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12183.944654399995,
          "startTime": 87.5333328247
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.7512938818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "何をコソコソ話してるんですかー？\nこころは暑いの苦手なので、先にお昼休憩入りまーす",
      "startTime": 81.866666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.132792314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、待ってよこころちゃーん！",
      "startTime": 89.132792314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7530667624
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7530667624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "さっき食べた『冷や汁』……凄く美味しかった……\nすみれちゃんのお母さん、ごちそうさまです",
      "startTime": 98.8030663332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.1364000958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "みんな明日はオフだから、今日はうちに泊まるって\nお母さんに言ったら、張り切ってお昼ご飯作ったみたい",
      "startTime": 105.630888637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8182596844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "山形の『だし』と、そうめんも最高でしたねー\nデザートのスイカも甘かったですし",
      "startTime": 113.8999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8664231938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "えっへん！\n山形の郷土料理はどれもとっても美味しいんだよ！",
      "startTime": 118.1790521464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4699608487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "自分のことのように喜んでますねー。さすが観光大使",
      "startTime": 122.4699608487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.6459701222
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.6883947533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "地元が褒められたら、嬉しいに決まってるよ～！\n山形の良さを、いっぱい知ってほしいっちゃ！",
      "startTime": 131.6883947533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1761878651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "不意に出る方言……高ポイント……\nすみれちゃん、可愛い……",
      "startTime": 138.1761874359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.1095211984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あざとい！　こうやってさりげなーく\nファンを獲得する訳ですか……なるほど",
      "startTime": 144.8333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7138074876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに深い意味はないよー！\nこころちゃん、分析しないでー！",
      "startTime": 151.9260052205,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9300.007009399991,
          "startTime": 161.2260122299
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.9260052205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "startTime": 155.3992245515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.4325477123
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.4325477123
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 160.9574241182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、こころちゃん、こっちこっち！\n暗いから足元気をつけてね",
      "startTime": 160.9574241182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.7538458507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "こんな暗い所に連れて来て、一体何をするつもりです？\nまさか……心霊スポットに連れてかれるんじゃ",
      "startTime": 169.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
